                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-24216",
                            "title": "Navigation menu updates",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>The main <b>Finance</b> menu includes functions to view finance related transactions.</p><p>Under the <b>Administration &gt; Feature settings</b> menu, the <b>Finance</b> menu includes functions to manage financial data.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "group",
                    "title": "Improvements",
                    "taxonomies": {
                        "_type": [
                            "changes"
                        ]
                    },
                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-16829",
                            "title": "Sequence number assignment",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>Under <b>Company data</b>, you can use the <b>Sequence number assignment</b> function for sales invoice documents. You can assign numbers to specific documents for a given legislation, company, and/or site. You can also search for sequence numbers that match this criteria.</p><p>Default sequence numbers are applied if you do not assign specific numbers.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "title": "Distribution",
            "id": "distribution",
            "type": "module",
            "content_parts": [
                {
                    "type": "group",
                    "title": "Features",
                    "taxonomies": {
                        "_type": [
                            "news"
                        ]
                    },
                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-22621",
                            "title": "Integrate A/P and A/R invoices with Sage Intacct for UK legislation",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>You can post A/P and A/R invoices and credit memos for sales and purchasing to Sage Intacct.</p><p>From the <b>Finance</b> menu, you access the related functions to view details and track the status. After an invoice is posted, you can select the <b>Accounting integration reference</b> number to go directly to that invoice in Sage Intacct.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-22619",
                            "title": "UK tax management setup ",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>For UK legislation, you can set up tax management including tax determination rules, tax calculation, and so on.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-20113",
                            "title": "Tax management on purchase receipts",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>You can assign tax rates on purchase receipt lines, such as tax determination rules, tax calculation, and tax management.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-17624",
                            "title": "Sending sales orders acknowledgements",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>From the <b>Sales order</b> function, you can send sales order details to an email recipient.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-6868",
                            "title": "Reorder point calculation",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>Use the <b>Stock reordering</b> function to generate purchase or work order recommendations for daily stock shortages from the current date to a specified end date. You can convert these recommendations into purchase or work orders based on the replenishment method and preferred process set on the item-site.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
